infoLinks.urlText: Palm Beach ferry diversion due to navigational restrictions
infoLinks.content: Ferries are diverting to Patonga. A free shuttle bus is running between Ettalong and Patonga wharves from 5:30am until 9:30am and from 3:30pm until 6:30pm Monday to Friday, and at different times throughout the weekend. The shuttle bus leaves about 35 minutes before the ferry leaves Patonga Wharf. Please be aware that Patonga Wharf is not wheelchair accessible. Plan ahead. More information can be found here.
